              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4>Rigor Científico</h4>
            <p>Fundamentamos nuestras decisiones en evidencia sólida y metodologías rigurosas para maximizar nuestro impacto.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M19 2H5C3.346 2 2 3.346 2 5V7.831C2 8.884 2.382 9.894 3.077 10.658L7.062 14.999L7 15C7 17.761 9.239 20 12 20C14.761 20 17 17.761 17 15L16.937 14.998L20.923 10.658C21.618 9.894 22 8.884 22 7.831V5C22 3.346 20.654 2 19 2ZM20 7.831C20 8.357 19.786 8.858 19.427 9.242L15.206 13.833C15.071 13.945 15 14.099 15 14.259V15C15 16.654 13.654 18 12 18C10.346 18 9 16.654 9 15V14.258C9 14.1 8.929 13.946 8.795 13.834L4.573 9.242C4.214 8.858 4 8.357 4 7.831V5C4 4.449 4.449 4 5 4H19C19.551 4 20 4.449 20 5V7.831ZM11 13.585V15C11 15.551 11.449 16 12 16C12.551 16 13 15.551 13 15V13.585L15.483 10.859L13.24 8.616C12.86 8.235 12.86 7.608 13.24 7.227C13.621 6.846 14.248 6.846 14.629 7.227L17.372 9.97C17.616 10.214 17.702 10.58 17.589 10.912C17.473 11.246 17.189 11.502 16.846 11.579C16.759 11.6 16.484 11.629 16.25 11.5L13 8.25V13.585H11Z" fill="currentColor"/>
