            <p>Tratamos a todos los individuos con igual consideración, independientemente de su ubicación, especies o generación.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M12 22C6.477 22 2 17.523 2 12C2 6.477 6.477 2 12 2C17.523 2 22 6.477 22 12C22 17.523 17.523 22 12 22ZM12 20C16.4183 20 20 16.4183 20 12C20 7.58172 16.4183 4 12 4C7.58172 4 4 7.58172 4 12C4 16.4183 7.58172 20 12 20ZM8 13H16C16 15.2091 14.2091 17 12 17C9.79086 17 8 15.2091 8 13ZM8 11C7.44772 11 7 10.5523 7 10C7 9.44772 7.44772 9 8 9C8.55228 9 9 9.44772 9 10C9 10.5523 8.55228 11 8 11ZM16 11C15.4477 11 15 10.5523 15 10C15 9.44772 15.4477 9 16 9C16.5523 9 17 9.44772 17 10C17 10.5523 16.5523 11 16 11Z" fill="currentColor"/>
